reviewText: Rare Film got for my mother as a gift !

Great movie for young and all and peanuts fans too a boy named Petey takes his stuffed dog to visit his grandpa only to lose it accidentally. Snoopy goes on lots of adventures on his Journey back to Petey Gets caught up with gangsters, Keeps company an old lady, gets bought by a carnie, gets won by a girl from a stall and attends a wedding. It's even got music in the background that sounds like as if it was a peanuts episode. Enjoy !
